# The ancient [[Greek language|Greek]] name of the country between the range of the [[Hindu Kush]] and the [[Amu Darya]] in the [[Middle East]], encompassing parts of northern [[Afghanistan]], eastern [[Turkmenistan]], southern [[Uzbekistan]], [[Tajikistan]] and northern [[Pakistan]].

